---
title: Mumbai Spiced Beef & Brown Rice Salad with Mint Yoghurt & Roasted Cashews
description: If you haven't tried brown rice, beef and veggies together, give this colourful bowl a go. Stirring fresh veggies and
spinach through this protein-rich grain brings it to life, while the addition of succulent spiced beef strips delivers a
nutritionally balanced meal everyone will love.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
